  * Add scons bindings= option and per-binding install targets (installpython, installjava, installcpp)
  * Extend CI pipeline with binding dependency installation and binding test step
  * Update org/package namespace from upstandinghackers to riversideresearch
  * Fix ParseResult double-free by making it move-only
  * Fix Python SWIG void*[] typemap memory leak and uint8_t single-byte validation

