libmicrohammer (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Microhammer, a slimmed-down subset of the Hammer parsing library.
  * Removed:
    - non-packrat backends
    - all language bindings
    - Windows/macOS support
    - Makefile build system
    - other non-essential files
  * Added / Improved:
    - improved documentation (consistent Doxygen for public API)
    - code style consistency (linting + formatting)
    - Debian packaging / build support

